preparationSteps:
Lower chauffer;
cuire for 5-10 minutes till peppers and tomatoes soften,
occasionally mixing

Retirer le couvercle;
augmenter le feu à moyen-vif; ajouter le poivre, le sel,
le paprika au goût et l'assaisonnement italien (ou pour volaille)

mélanger garlic and olive oil into the water and pasta;
keep cooking for about 11 minutes jusqu'à ce que fully cooked but still
firm when bitten into; strain

Put crushed tomatoes in skillet;
assaisonner with parsley, pepper, oregano, garlic powder, bay leaf
and Italian seasoning

Working in batches, cuire for 15 minutes
till cooked completely and deep golden brown on every side;
put to big serving plate

Using an electric mixer, beat butter for 2 minutes jusqu'à ce que fluffy;
beat in white sugar and brown sugar for 1 minute, jusqu'à ce que the
mixture is smooth

Spread the
mixture over on the top of cherry tomatoes in baking sheet;
drizzle the remaining 5 tablespoons of olive oil over
